data.text:
Awọn apẹẹrẹ: feyenoord

Feyenoord were thus knocked of the Champions League and demoted to the Europa League. Bayi Feyenoord ni wọn ti kọlu ti Awọn aṣaju-ija Champions League ati pe o lọ silẹ si Ajumọṣe Yuroopu. Bastos started his career at hometown club Pelotas before moving to the Netherlands, where he played for Feyenoord and Excelsior. Bastos bẹrẹ iṣẹ rẹ ni ilu Pelotas club ṣaaju ki o to lọ si Fiorino, nibiti o ti ṣere fun Feyenoord ati Excelsior. After spending most of the previous two seasons out on loan, Manu broke into the Feyenoord first team during the 2014–15 season, becoming a regular for the club. Lẹhin lilo pupọ julọ awọn akoko meji ti tẹlẹ lori awin, Manu fọ sinu ẹgbẹ akọkọ Feyenoord lakoko akoko 2014 – 15, di deede fun ẹgbẹ naa. Born in Kumasi, Asare has played for Feyenoord Fetteh, Feyenoord, Royal Antwerp, Mechelen, Utrecht and Gent. Ti a bi ni Kumasi, Asare ti ṣere fun Feyenoord Fetteh, Feyenoord, Royal Antwerp, Mechelen, Utrecht ati Gent. After progressing through Feyenoord's youth academy, Manu signed a professional contract with the club in 2012. Lẹhin ilọsiwaju nipasẹ ile-ẹkọ ọdọ ọdọ Feyenoord, Manu fowo si iwe adehun alamọdaju pẹlu ẹgbẹ ni ọdun 2012. After returning to Feyenoord at the beginning of 2013–14 season, Manu was loaned out once again on 9 January 2014, joining Eredivise side SC Cambuur until the end of the season. Lẹhin ipadabọ si Feyenoord ni ibẹrẹ akoko 2013 – 14, Manu ti ya awin lekan si ni ọjọ 9 Oṣu Kini ọdun 2014, darapọ mọ ẹgbẹ Eredivise SC Cambuur titi di opin akoko naa. After being released by Feyenoord, he joined Eerste Divisie team Almere City in 2013. Lẹhin idasilẹ nipasẹ Feyenoord, o darapọ mọ ẹgbẹ Eerste Divisie Almere City ni ọdun 2013. Larsson won his first major winner's medal on 12 May 1994 when he played in the Feyenoord side that defeated NEC 2–1 in the final of the KNVB Cup. Larsson gba ami-eye olubori akọkọ akọkọ rẹ ni 12 May 1994 nigbati o ṣere ni ẹgbẹ Feyenoord ti o ṣẹgun NEC 2–1 ni ipari ti KNVB Cup. A youth product of FC Groningen, Kökçü joined the Feyenoord youth academy in 2014. Ọja ọdọ ti FC Groningen, Kökçü darapọ mọ ile-iwe ọdọ ọmọde ti Feyenoord ni 2014. On 24 August 2017, Manchester City were drawn into Group F alongside Shakhtar Donetsk, Napoli and Feyenoord. Ni ọjọ 24 Oṣu Kẹjọ ọdun 2017, Manchester City ni iyaworan sinu Group F lẹgbẹẹ Shakhtar Donetsk, Napoli ati Feyenoord. In July 2005, Adams accepted a trainee coaching role with Dutch side Feyenoord with special responsibility for its Jong team, which is a reserve/junior side. Ni Oṣu Keje ọdun 2005, Adams gba ipa ikẹkọ olukọni pẹlu ẹgbẹ Dutch Feyenoord pẹlu ojuse pataki fun ẹgbẹ Jong rẹ, eyiti o jẹ ibi ipamọ / ẹgbẹ kekere. In November 1993, Dutch side Feyenoord signed Larsson for a fee of £295,000. Ni Oṣu kọkanla ọdun 1993, ẹgbẹ Dutch Feyenoord fowo si Larsson fun idiyele ti £ 295,000. Davids signed once more for Ajax on 28 January 2007 and played his first match against club rivals Feyenoord on 4 February. Davids fowo si lẹẹkan si fun Ajax ni ọjọ 28 Oṣu Kini ọdun 2007 ati pe o ṣe ere akọkọ rẹ si awọn abanidije ẹgbẹ Feyenoord ni ọjọ 4 Kínní.
